    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1747235694\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1747235694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/bed0effd09eb5cd0d9633c2d44517af5.poster.avif?t=1747235694\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/bed0effd09eb5cd0d9633c2d44517af5.webm?t=1747235694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/bed0effd09eb5cd0d9633c2d44517af5.mp4?t=1747235694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>《Kalyzmyr（卡利兹梅尔）》是一个关于传奇战士士麦娜逃出名为卡利兹梅尔的地下城的小游戏，拥有漂亮的手绘像素图像，是一款横向卷轴动作游戏。它将塔防、地下城探险和砍杀等流行玩法元素简单地结合在一起，并添加了大量按键狂按、随机的互动和战利品。每一轮大概会用30-60分钟，还为速通者提供了计时器。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/eb8b5ff202b25e70423e0db948f56ba8.poster.avif?t=1747235694\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/eb8b5ff202b25e70423e0db948f56ba8.webm?t=1747235694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/eb8b5ff202b25e70423e0db948f56ba8.mp4?t=1747235694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>曾经的传奇战士士麦娜，如今早已被遗忘在卡利兹梅尔的深处。打破你的枷锁，获得自由！用你坚不可摧的战斧，干掉把你锁在卡利兹梅尔的敌人！<br><br>在这款老派的快节奏动作游戏中，你可以在成群的恶魔中突出重围。<br>每一层都有一个防御阶段，玩家可以通过购买和升级防御装备来抵御成群的怪物。杀死怪物来赚钱，开战利品箱来升级你的装备。 </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/d26afc38071a186c9a53c7d279c65c6d.poster.avif?t=1747235694\" width=600 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/d26afc38071a186c9a53c7d279c65c6d.webm?t=1747235694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/d26afc38071a186c9a53c7d279c65c6d.mp4?t=1747235694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>塞翁失马，焉知非福<br>互动物品是随机生成的，每个都可能减轻你的负担或惩罚你。祈求好运吧，你会需要的。</strong><br><br><strong>觉得虚弱吗？还是不太走运？任何时候都可以破门回到上一层。在低层锻炼自己，收集奖励，并准备面对更强大的对手。 </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/f4c54b79077251cac016776692302e7d.poster.avif?t=1747235694\" width=623 height=471 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/f4c54b79077251cac016776692302e7d.webm?t=1747235694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>14种不同的敌人和3个独特的Boss</strong><br><strong>每个关卡都有一个独特的Boss和不同的怪物，以及更厉害的奖励掉落和新的装备。</strong><br><br><strong>释放你真正的力量</strong><br><strong>通过激活狂暴模式释放士麦娜的真正潜力，让你的攻击速度比任何东西都快。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/7d8f9a57e15148c269679e925c097e24.poster.avif?t=1747235694\" width=600 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/7d8f9a57e15148c269679e925c097e24.webm?t=1747235694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826090/extras/7d8f9a57e15148c269679e925c097e24.mp4?t=1747235694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
